title: MI Gov. Whitmer: I Don’t Regret State Lockdown Policy Despite Protests
description: Sunday on NBC's "Meet the Press," Gov. Gretchen Whitmer (D-MI) said she has no regrets on any of the restrictions of her stay home order in response to the coronavirus pandemic despite the protests in her state. | Clips
